      "id": "PopularPost65470",
      "post_content": "Not sure what a curvaceous Kor with a penchant for belts has to do with the effect, but whatever.  \n  \nKind of expensive for the effect, even knowing that most comparable cards have a restriction not of your choosing.  \n  \nAlso compare to [Circle of Affliction](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Circle of Affliction), which requires you to continuously pay for the affect, but lets you aim it, and is a drain effect on top of that.",
